name: Hoodrats Creed
description:
Ownership of this token symbolizes the agreement to the counter strike pact and commitment to the Creed.

Failure to uphold Creed values will result in a temporary queue ban with the Elite Gaming Squadron that is The Tactical Hoodrat Squadron until moral improves.

This creed was ratified at 8:40 PM EST on March 7th, 2022.
